== Usage ==
<pre>
{{Infobox_Scientist
| lagyu = (Insert name of scientist, mathematician or engineer)
| image = (Insert *.jpg image preferably at 300px)
| image_width = (Optional; Insert image width)
| caption = (Insert photograph caption. Try to include date of photo and the photographer)
| aldo kebaitan = (Insert date of birth: month, day, year)
| lugal kebaitan = (Insert place of birth: town, city, country)
| aldo kematyan = (Insert date of death: month, day, year)
| lugal kematyan = (Insert place of death: town, city, country)
| tuknanagan = (Insert countries where scientist has lived. If some are minor, select key countries)
| nationality = (Insert nationality of scientist)
| marangle = (State if they are a physicist, chemist, biologist, mathematician, engineer....)
| work_institution = (Insert key companies and/or universities where they are/were employed)
| alma_mater = (Insert universities where they obtained their degrees)
| talausuk a doctoral= (Insert doctoral advisor. If no PhD, can put in equivalent accepted mentors. Then use footnote to explain.)
| magarala doctoral = (If any, insert their key doctoral or notable students. Does not have to be exhaustive.)
| bantug   = (Insert key topics/areas of science that made them famous)
| galal = (Insert most notable prizes and medals.)
| kasalpantayanan = (Insert religious belief system/affiliation. The consensus is to use this field sparingly.)
| footnotes = (Insert any extra details here. Especially point out a notable parent or child to link to their wiki pages)
}}

</pre>

